<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>JDBB</title>

    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;500;700&display=swap');

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background: #0b0b0c;
            color: #e6e6e6;
        }

        header {
            padding: 25px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 10;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 32px;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1594069758873-8f7c2d0bbd10?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1950&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hero::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.55);
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* ↓↓↓ ONLY CHANGE #1: text size reduced by 2px ↓↓↓ */
        .hero-content h2 {
            font-size: 62px; /* was 64px */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        /* ↑↑↑ ONLY CHANGE #1 ↑↑↑ */

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 20px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .section {
            padding: 80px 40px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: auto;
        }

        .section h3 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 25px;
            background: #000;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 60px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <h1>JDBB</h1>
</header>

<div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
        <h2>Strength. Precision. Presence.</h2>
        <p>JDBB delivers modern solutions with an edge — built for those who lead, not follow.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h3>About JDBB</h3>
    <p>
        JDBB represents a commitment to excellence, discipline, and forward‑thinking execution.
        Whether you're building, scaling, or refining, JDBB stands for power and precision.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h3>Contact</h3>
    <p>Email: contact@jdbb.us</p>
</div>

<div class="footer">
    © 2026 JDBB — All Rights Reserved
</div>

</body>
</html>
